{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"36678-rat-and-goat","title":"Rat and Goat","description":"Rat loves to play hopscotch but he has no one to play with. His neighbour, Goat, is at home but he prefers to be alone. Can Rat persuade Goat to play with him?","language":"English","langCode":"en","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Sanjana  Khoobchandani"],"illustrators":["Try Samphors"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Room to Read","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/36678-rat-and-goat"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/101334/size3/34ea188d375dede8e22508a9013dc8eb.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/101334/size6/34ea188d375dede8e22508a9013dc8eb.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/69865/size6/addc33e2ff3a8deefe571bd1e24d2030.jpg","text":"Rat loves to play outside.","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/69866/size6/06c70b427cff7462fb5f4431d653c9a2.jpg","text":"Today he wants to play Moek (hopscotch), but there is nobody to play with.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/69867/size6/deebc8fdcc69ea6357218e118059650f.jpg","text":"“I have an idea,”  he thinks. \n“\nI'll invite Goat, my neighbour.\n”","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/69868/size6/0dafa76545619297c5240ce8c1c0637d.jpg","text":"Goat likes to spend time alone, fishing and napping.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/69869/size6/abad02841affe5368b1b4b8e983e9735.jpg","